posting_body: ['Single Story Apartment, Private Garage, Wood Floors, Wall A/C, Fresh Paint!', 'Property Address', '765 Nevin Way - 1 | San Jose, CA 95128', 'Offered By', 'Presidential Real Estate, Inc |', 'show contact info', 'Description', '765 Nevin Way #1, San Jose, CA 95128 (Southwest Exp/Fruitdale)', 'Spacious 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, single story home.', ' The home is in a small 3 unit building located in central San Jose and has been renovated to include wood flooring, fresh paint inside and out, new baseboards, and new window coverings.', ' The eat-in kitchen has wood cabinets with granite counters, a built in oven, flat top stove, and a fridge.', 'A spacious living room with fireplace and wall air conditioner.', ' The bedrooms include overhead lighting and mirror closet doors.', ' The elegant bathrooms were previously updated.', 'The home comes with a 1 car private garage with 1 additional driveway space.', 'Water is included with the rent.', '1 year lease required.', 'No pets except for required service animals.', 'The home is located near San Jose City College and theVTA lightrail/bus service and within minutes of highway 280, 880, and central Expressway.', 'Cal DRE# 01998337', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 3BD/2.0BA', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $3,275.00', 'Application Fee: $25.00', 'Security Deposit: $3,000.00']
